{"tid":2028152,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［黑色五毛警報現正生效］","createTime":"2020-05-21T16:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T09:23:58.000Z","uid":232594,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f00ed137bf66f3057c6bd0ee42e614f89327767f","tid":2028152,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:18:13.000Z","msg":"人大一傳會繞過香港立國安法，連登五毛空群而出進行各種分化<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請記住不分化不割蓆</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n呢個係一直以黎令我地團結既意志<br />\n<br />\n好似頭條新聞豪仔咁講，投票又好唔投票又好，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有我地可以做既野我地盡量做</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拒絕任何分化</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2144359bb856957b352c52e24fc12c8138f4227d","tid":2028152,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">能夠做既盡做<br />\n拒絕任何分化</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c148fa6f5845a20db527cba83783f188088d1001","tid":2028152,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">能夠做既盡做<br />\n拒絕任何分化</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"113b2876339508a1892d3e747606b689fd7a6a0c","tid":2028152,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">能夠做既盡做<br />\n拒絕任何分化</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"547fa5ea68ab527427c1d6ffad539d43f33e95ce","tid":2028152,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"投票又其他野又好，能夠做既盡做，拒絕任何分化"},{"pid":"e667930d1f0b9db35ae098eeddb92aafc2cbfe43","tid":2028152,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"投票又其他野又好，能夠做既盡做